Opp.: <term xml:lang="jpa">אימירון</term>
               <term xml:lang="fjb">ʾymyrwn</term> |emeron| 
(used together in: NumR 11,3 [= ShirR 3,5; PesK 1, MShem 17,4]).
   </note>
